\begin_layout Abstract
This is a survey of some key steps in document preparation with LyX.
 It is intended to facilitate the user's transition from a first-time LyX
 user to usage of special features that are necessary to make truly professional
-quality documents.
 It also offers advice about interacting with the LyX user interface.
 
\end_layout

