\begin_layout Standard
\align left
This document is a collection of important tips and tricks for authors who
 are making the transition from Microsoft Word (or similar) to the more
 structured document preparation framework known as LaTeX.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align left
We'd like to start by criticizing MS Word, but only briefly.
 We expect most people who find this document already know what's wrong
 with Word.
 Its terrible.
 Many users report severe frustration when trying to format a document in
 a consistent (and seemingly simple) way.
 Users have questions like 
